# Flask-React Portfolio

## Project Overview

This project is a personal portfolio website built using Flask for the backend and React for the frontend. The portfolio showcases projects, provides a resume, and gives a brief introduction to the developer, Fernando Duffoo. The site features smooth scrolling and a clean, modern design to present your work and credentials professionally.

